  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  HIV Infected Children under 60 months of age presenting at HIV treatment clinics in
             Dar es Salaam, Tanzania

        Exclusion Criteria:

        Eligible for ART: CD4 cell counts &lt; 20% or above pediatric clinical stage of HIV disease 3
        according to WHO staging system.

        Severe acute malnutrition; Major congenital malformations
      </textblock>
